snippet.title: Heartland's Amber Marshall Swims with Horses | Heartland | CBC
snippet.description:
Go behind-the-scenes of Heartland with Amber Marshall, who talks about her past experience swimming with horses, and how Heartland attempted to portray that in season 8, episode 12. Subscribe: http://bit.ly/CBCSubscribe
Watch Full Episodes of Heartland: http://bit.ly/FullEpisodesCBC 

About Heartland: Heartland is a family drama on CBC TV about a family dealing with the highs and lows of life on a horse ranch in the stunning the foothills of Alberta.
